# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# MINISTRY CHECKOUT v4 — Environment Variables
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
# HOW TO USE THIS FILE:
#   Local dev  → cp .env.local.example .env.local  → fill in your values
#   Production → Vercel Dashboard → Project → Settings → Environment Variables
#                paste each variable name + value there (no quotes needed)
#
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════


# ── GCash Merchant Details ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# These are shown on every checkout page so customers know where to send money.
NEXT_PUBLIC_GCASH_NUMBER=0951 251 8441
NEXT_PUBLIC_GCASH_NAME=J. Balasa
#
# IMPORTANT: Save your GCash QR code image to /public/gcash/qr.png
# How: GCash app → Profile → QR Code → Download/Share → save the image
# Customers can scan it OR tap the "Download QR" button on mobile.


# ── Verification Settings ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
NEXT_PUBLIC_CURRENCY=PHP
#
# PRICE_TOLERANCE: how many pesos of rounding error to allow.
# Example: price=497, tolerance=5 → accepts ₱492–₱502
PRICE_TOLERANCE=5
#
# TEST_MODE=true  → skips amount/date/QR checks (use for local testing only!)
# TEST_MODE=false → full strict verification (REQUIRED in production)
TEST_MODE=true


# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# PER-PRODUCT CONFIGURATION
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
# Each product needs 3 env vars:
#   NEXT_PUBLIC_PRODUCT_{SLUG}_PRICE      = price in PHP (integer)
#   PRODUCT_FILE_URL_{SLUG}               = Mediafire direct download URL
#   NEXT_PUBLIC_DOWNLOAD_PAGE_URL_{SLUG}  = Systeme.io thank-you/download page
#
# HOW TO GET A MEDIAFIRE DIRECT DOWNLOAD LINK:
#   1. Upload your zip file to mediafire.com
#   2. Right-click the file → Copy Download Link
#      OR: open the file → click "Download" → copy the URL from the redirect
#      The URL starts with: https://download###.mediafire.com/...
#   3. Paste the full URL as PRODUCT_FILE_URL_{SLUG} below
#
# HOW TO ADD A NEW PRODUCT IN THE FUTURE:
#   1. Add 3 env vars below (copy any block as template)
#   2. Add 1 entry in src/app/api/download-token/route.ts  (getProductUrls map)
#   3. Add 1 entry in src/app/api/verify-receipt/route.ts  (getPriceForProduct map)
#   4. Create src/app/products/{slug}/page.tsx using ProductPageTemplate
#   Done — no other files need changing.
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════


